<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>the planetary's fundamental underlying operating system.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742000' id='t-742000'>So when we see E equals mc squared come along, from a poet's perspective,</span>
